title: AP PHOTOS: A selection of pictures from the past week
text:
Here's your look at highlights from the weekly AP photo report, a gallery featuring a mix of front-page photography, the odd image you might have missed and lasting moments our editors think you should see.
This week's gallery includes a tearful reunion of North and South Korean relatives; demonstrators seeking cover from tear gas in Bahrain; and migrants warming themselves in thermal blankets after arriving in Greece.
___
This gallery contains photos published Oct. 17-23, 2015.
See the latest AP photo galleries: http://apne.ws/TXeCBN
The Archive: Top photo highlights from previous weeks: http://apne.ws/13QUFKJ
